{
  "text": "We recall that a double category is fibrant in the terminology of [CITATION_1] if every vertical 1-morphism has a companion and a conjoint. These are horizontal 1-morphisms that allow transport of vertical structure to horizontal structure [Shu10, \u00a73]:",
